1.1.1	Im helping a person set up a business where people with &quot;subscriptions&quot; can come in and work.	St
1.1.2	We plan to have wireless as part of it.	St
1.1.3	However, we want a system whereby we can give them accounts with passwords that, when the subscription ends, we can disable.	St
1.1.4	Ive used vpns that had this functionality in a corporation I worked at, but Im at a loss as to what would work best for a small business.	St
